---
title: Sarh — Property submission, review, manager approval, NFT minting, and verify
---
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor C as Citizen
    actor O as Registry officer
    actor M as Department<br/>Manager
    participant W as apps/web (Angular)
    participant API as .NET 8 API
    participant DB as SQL Server
    participant FS as Storage<br/>(local FS)
    participant PDF as PAdES signer
    participant SSI as ACA-Py<br/>(Hyperledger Aries)
    participant IPFS as IPFS<br/>(metadata pin)
    participant BC as Blockchain<br/>(Ethereum / Hyperledger)
    participant SC as Smart Contract<br/>(ERC-721)
    actor V as Public verifier

    rect rgb(239, 246, 255)
    Note over C,DB: 1) Submission
    C->>W: fill form + draw polygon
    W->>API: POST /api/v1/properties { polygon, area, docs }
    API->>DB: INSERT properties (status='pending')
    API->>DB: INSERT registration_requests
    DB-->>API: property_id, request_no
    API-->>W: 201 SubmitResult
    end

    rect rgb(254, 252, 232)
    Note over O,DB: 2) Officer review (technical + spatial)
    O->>W: open /app/queue
    W->>API: GET /api/v1/properties?status=pending
    API->>DB: SELECT
    DB-->>W: list
    O->>W: open detail, read docs, view map, run conflict check
    O->>W: click "Recommend approval" + technical note
    W->>API: POST /api/v1/properties/:id/review { decision: 'recommend_approval' }
    API->>DB: UPDATE properties SET status='under_review',<br/>reviewed_by_officer_id
    DB->>DB: AFTER UPDATE trigger → audit_log INSERT
    end

    rect rgb(252, 231, 243)
    Note over M,DB: 3) Department Manager final approval
    M->>W: open /app/approvals
    W->>API: GET /api/v1/properties?status=under_review
    API->>DB: SELECT
    DB-->>W: list
    M->>W: review officer recommendation + decree no
    M->>W: click "Final approve"
    W->>API: POST /api/v1/properties/:id/final-approve { approval_decree_no }
    API->>DB: UPDATE properties SET status='approved',<br/>approved_by_manager_id, approval_decree_no
    DB->>DB: audit_log INSERT
    end

    rect rgb(236, 253, 245)
    Note over API,SSI: 4) Deed PDF + SSI VC issuance
    API->>PDF: generate deed PDF<br/>(citizen, polygon, decree)
    PDF-->>API: signed PAdES bytes + SHA256
    API->>FS: write deeds/<id>.pdf
    API->>DB: UPDATE properties SET deed_pdf_path, deed_signed_hash
    API->>SSI: issue VC (PropertyDeed) for citizen DID
    SSI-->>API: credential_id
    API->>DB: UPDATE properties SET vc_credential_id
    end

    rect rgb(224, 231, 255)
    Note over API,SC: 5) NFT licence minting on blockchain
    API->>API: build token metadata<br/>(propertyCode, polygon GeoJSON,<br/>deed SHA256, ownerDID, decree)
    API->>IPFS: pin metadata.json
    IPFS-->>API: ipfs://Qm…CID
    API->>BC: mint(toAddress, tokenId, tokenURI)
    BC->>SC: invoke mint()
    SC-->>BC: Transfer(0x0, owner, tokenId)
    BC-->>API: txHash + blockNumber
    API->>DB: INSERT property_nfts<br/>(token_id, contract, network, metadata_uri,<br/>mint_tx_hash, minted_by_manager_id)
    API->>DB: INSERT ownership_history<br/>(from=null, to=owner_did, reason='initial_mint')
    API->>DB: UPDATE properties SET status='minted'
    API->>DB: INSERT notifications (citizen, "deed + NFT licence ready")
    end

    rect rgb(254, 226, 226)
    Note over C,V: 6) Delivery + public verify (PDF + on-chain)
    C->>W: open /app/my/properties → download PDF + view NFT
    W->>API: GET /api/v1/storage/deeds/<id>.pdf
    API->>FS: read file
    FS-->>C: PDF (with QR pointing to /verify/<code>)

    V->>W: scan QR / open /verify/<code>
    W->>API: GET /api/v1/verify/:code
    API->>DB: SELECT property + verify hash + nft
    API->>BC: ownerOf(tokenId)
    BC-->>API: current owner address
    API-->>V: 200 { owner, area, decree, signed: true,<br/>nft: { tokenId, contract, network, txHash, currentOwner } }
    end
